                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A self serving treatise by a convicted con-man</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>1</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>0</span>
                      /
